## ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» Usage
Commands avialable to xeni:
```bash
xeni start #starts the FastAPI server

xeni connect ${agent_name} #Connect to supported agents

xeni key ${API_key} --token ${Bearer token} #Sets the user credentials

xeni set-url ${url}
```
